<doc id="243948" wikidata="Q8052111" url="?curid=243948" title="Yemenite">
<text>Yemenite (Arabic: يماني‎, romanized: &quot;Yamāni&quot;) is someone whose ancestors are from Yemen, or something that is linked to Yemen. It may refer to:

*Al-Yamani, a pre-messianic figure in Shia Islamic eschatology
*Yemenite Hebrew, dialect of the Hebrew language
*Yemenite Jews
*Yemenite Kaaba
*Yemenite step, an Israeli folk dance step originating from Yemen
*Yemenis, diaspora of Yemen

