* Olson, Storrs L. (1985): Section X.D.2.b. &quot;Scolopacidae&quot;. In: Farner, D.S.; King, J.R. &amp; Parkes, Kenneth C. (eds.): &quot;Avian Biology&quot; 8: 174–175. Academic Press, New York.</text><links>
